Basic Installation
==================

aKode relies on cmake to build.

Here are suggested default options:

 -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RelWithDebInfo \
 -DCMAKE_VERBOSE_MAKEFILE="ON" \
 -DCMAKE_SKIP_RPATH="OFF" \
 -DWITH_ALL_OPTIONS="ON"



Optional:
=========
 - Alsa
 - PulseAudio
 - Flac
 - Libmad
 - Libogg/Libvorbis
 - Speex
 - Lisamplerate
 - JACK Audio Connection Kit
